  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.amidst.latentvariablemodels.staticmodels.Model
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BayesianLinearRegression, Classifier, CustomGaussianMixture, FactorAnalysis, GaussianMixture, LDA, MixtureOfFactorAnalysers

    public abstract class Model
extends Object
    The Model abstract class is defined as a superclass to all static standard models (not used for classification, if so, extends Classifier) Created by andresmasegosa on 4/3/16.
